com.psddev.dari.util

Interface ImageEditor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SettingsBackedObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractImageEditor, DimsImageEditor

    public interface ImageEditor
extends SettingsBackedObject
    Image editor can manipulate an image item in a storage system. Typically, this is used to crop or resize an image.
